Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真子和大谷好像都感冒請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,相比之下 我就一直很健康...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能... 我身為笨蛋怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你也讓人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小森拒絕不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:17.62,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\c&H26302A&\3c&HF5F6F6&\3a&H00&\fs72\pos(1175.333,244)}第\N二\N天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:18.16,Default top,,0,0,0,,小惠也請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.24,Default top,,0,0,0,,小森
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.00,DefaultScroller,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,681.333)}能幫忙把講義拿去給請假的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:22.96,DefaultScroller,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,682.667)}好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.75,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0F0F0F&\3c&HFDFDFD&\3a&H00&\pos(1010,400.667)}小惠爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:24.75,DefaultScroller,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,677.333)}應該是讀書讀太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.88,DefaultScroller,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.333,685.333)}她說一定要和朋友考上同一所高中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.13,DefaultScroller,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,685.333)}有那麼好的朋友是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.18,DefaultScroller,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,682.667)}要不要抱抱她會比較好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 朱梨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我們永遠都是朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會慢慢就疏遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但現在也只能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的 我最喜歡你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真像你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,來了來了 哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,終於結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明天請假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}馬上就要畢業了 請一天假太可惜了{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}而且 感覺好寂寞{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,吵醒你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是我傳給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不舒服?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可能是我傳染給她了 去探望她一下吧{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}為什麼?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}只要去想就會一下不安一下放心{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}但都沒有問題 一定會有能讓人開心起來的藥{\i0}
